    "path": "src/agent/task",
    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime state. Task keeps public construction, preview, worker routing, and direct session_tx event sending in task.rs; TaskState stores the original user request, step_count, steps, and a PlanQueue-backed plan_queue. task_step.rs triggers the initial Plan from user_request, confines add_plan to run_plan, inserts plans into PlanQueue with globally allocated StepSignatures, runs queued signatures, routes model completion to Answer or Plan parsing, sends TaskStatus::Succeed for Answer results, and records completed steps through PlanQueue::complete_step.",
